{"tid":1225803,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「林鄭記者會」點解啲記者問題 好似默認左中央係可以對香港內部問題說三道四？","createTime":"2019-06-15T08:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T11:43:03.000Z","uid":7093,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ade01ffc75742c473ef7753df46eeb244e5e2dca","tid":1225803,"uid":7093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:36:05.000Z","msg":"作為一個90後，我自細聽既學既<br />\n係「港人治港，高度自治」<br />\n除左軍事 同 外交<br />\n其他都係我地話事<br />\n<br />\n由幾時開始，大家好似接受左中國政府<br />\n係可以對其他事務有好大既話語權既呢？<br />\n<br />\n每一個記者提問，都係講緊<br />\n「覺唔覺對中央添煩添亂」<br />\n「有無得到中央支持？」<br />\n<br />\n呢條修例 無論點計都係local exercise <br />\n大家咁做根本係潛意識已經係度矮化自己<br />\n久而久之 就對呢件事習以為常<br />\n<br />\n呢個 唔係一個大問題咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328ce2cd52219e045e4c27fee927d819245d4e31","tid":1225803,"uid":132770,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"已經係直接指標揮"},{"pid":"397738eb073829cb0e9f245ed028d03699b02823","tid":1225803,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:38:02.000Z","msg":"明顯聽得出中央同佢講咗唔想再見到有衝突發生，叫佢自己執生...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f79460b6a75bc260b23ee44c960ebd4d5ec303","tid":1225803,"uid":7093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:38:34.000Z","msg":"中央有最終話事權呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n暗啞底 同 擺上枱<br />\n差好遠下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我淨係好擔心<br />\n<br />\n我地下一代係呢個環境 呢個自我矮化既環境<br />\n<br />\n已經唔知根據基本法同中英聯合聲明 我地根本就無需要理中央"},{"pid":"1526000a028543c38ec4dba28a475d4230bc5261","tid":1225803,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:38:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.privacytools.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.privacytools.io%2F&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=f263e6f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.privacytools.io